data.description: Absolutely Beautiful....Vaulted ceilings in the Great Room with a few landings/ displays...large master bedroom and master bath with garden tub, split bedroom plan with nice size bedrooms and bath, Nice size kitchen and dining room...French doors from the kitchen to covered deck outside, great lot with view, large level fenced back yard, 12x24 storage building, sodded front yard. Beautifully decorated with upgraded lighting and faucets and only one mile and less to Hayden schools. Beautifully perched above the road with stunning views. Homeowner was in the process of new flooring in bedrooms but will give a flooring allowance with acceptable offer. Just in time for the Holidays!
